Class::DBI::ToSax
=================

This module provides a direct-to-XML facility for Class::DBI objects.
It is used as part of a SAX pipeline.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  NEXT (any version)
  Class::Data::Inheritable (any version)
  Class::Accessor (any version)
  XML::SAX::Writer (any version)

XML::SAX::Writer is only required for the tests, but most users of this
module will end up using it, I feel.

